
COMMAND:
   mood or mood <argument> 

ART:
   With the command mood you get the menue of the combat modes
   you may take. Mood aggressive for example sets your mode to
   aggressive. That means you have more attacks but a very bad 
   dodge. Current moods are: aggressive, moderate, defensive.

   WARNING ! If you are in the aggressive mood you are very
   easy and hard to hit.

COST:
   none 

